		<p style="text-align: center;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Communal enterprise ?Agency of Regional Development and Cross-Border Co-operation ?Transcarpathia? of Zakarpattya Oblast Council?</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>ARD ?Transcarpathia? &nbsp;was established by Zakarpattya Oblast Council on January 11, 2002.</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">The main goal of establishment of the Enterprise is to support local authorities, NGOs and business structures in implementation of programmes and projects directed to sustainable socio-economic development of the region, its separate parts and sectors of the national economy.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Main tasks:</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">? &nbsp; &nbsp; Developing of cross-border co-operation in the Carpathian Euroregion</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">? &nbsp; &nbsp; Contributing to regional and local development in Zakarpatska oblast</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">? &nbsp; &nbsp; Attracting of investments and international technical assistance into the region</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>The activities of the ARD ?Transcarpathia? are as follows:</strong></span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>&nbsp;</strong>- &nbsp; &nbsp; development and implementation of regional development program as well as specific sectorial and territorial projects;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; contributing to advanced training of specialists in regional development and project managers of organizations;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; contributing to integration processes through establishing and strengthening direct contacts with organizations and authorities of Ukraine, EU member-states, candidate countries and leading structures of the EU;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; contributing to development, initiation and implementation of joint cross-border projects;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; co-operation with local authorities in elaboration and implementation of programmes and projects;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; development of the complex of measures directed to establishing of positive image of the region and its investment attractiveness;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; promotion of the region towards its potential consumers ? international donor and financial institutions;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; involving of international and national financial institutions into participation in the development of Zakarpattya, solving of socio-economic problems of the region, activation of investment and business activity;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; assisting to companies in attracting of foreign investments;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; forming of the unified information space, information networks and databases;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; forming of the database of projects and programmes that are being developed or implemented in Zakarpattya;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp; contributing to synchronization of the EU technical assistance programmes and programmes of other donor organizations aimed at increasing the possibilities of regional development institutions in implementing of joint cross-border projects;</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">- &nbsp; &nbsp;conducting of complex research aimed at defining priority directions of development of Zakarpatska oblast and border regions of neighbouring countries.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">The Agency has developed dozens of publications on cross-border co-operation that were disseminated free of charge on the territories of Ukraine, Slovakia, Hungary and Romania since 2002.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">A list of international, regional and local conferences and seminars were organized and carried out with participation of the Agency. Study visits for representatives of Zakarpatska oblast to neighbouring countries of the Carpathian Euroregion and countries of the Western Europe were organized. Acquaintance tours for representatives of foreign partner organizations to Zakarpattya were also carried out by the Agency.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: justify;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;">The Agency organized series of trainings and study programmes for representatives of different target groups of Zakarpattya (authorities, nonprofit and non-governmental organizations, students and youth, etc.) with participation of the best international specialists both on and outside the territory of Ukraine.</span></p>
<p style="text-align: left;"><span style="font-family: arial,helvetica,sans-serif; font-size: 10pt;"><strong>Communal enterprise:</strong> "Agency of Regional Development and Cross-Border Co-operation</span></p>
